| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0454 — Recovery Inhibition (devman)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4f26ce82-c2e5-5704-8fbf-1caa0cb0c6c2"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
